</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_100" id="49v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_100_r1l1">Margraf Jobſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l2">von Merhern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_100_r1l3"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / von der habe vnd kauffmanſchaft wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l4">Als den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vorcʒeite<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat cʒu Prunne ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l5">nomen iſt vvoꝛden / Darümb ~ die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Pawlus Jm hof </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l6"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd vlrıch Ryſbecken gevvalt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l7">Als ſie <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden ſelber wol <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> werden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l8"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ewr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade darcʒu vvenden vnd <expan>ſchike<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l9">vnd <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet / daʒ den ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dieſelb Jr habe vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l10">kauffmanſchaft gnedıklich gekert vnd vergolten werde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_100_r1l11">Als vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_100" id="49v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Margraf Jobsen von Merhern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, von der habe und kauffmanschaft wegen, als
                        den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vorczeite<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> stat czu
                        Prunne genomen ist worden, darümb die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Pawlus
                        Im hof, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, und Ulrich Rysbecken gewalt
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als sie <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                        selber wol <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> werden.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir ewr
                            <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade darczu wenden und
                                <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, daz den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dieselb ir habe und kauffmanschaft
                        gnediklich gekert und vergolten werde, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
